query:
SELECT
                l.id as "id!: Uuid",
                l.project_id as "project_id: Uuid",
                l.name,
                l.icon,
                l.color,
                l.created_at as "created_at!: DateTime<Utc>",
                l.updated_at as "updated_at!: DateTime<Utc>"
            FROM labels l
            INNER JOIN task_labels tl ON l.id = tl.label_id
            WHERE tl.task_id = $1
            ORDER BY l.name ASC
